# Motion simulator (motion_simulator flat ride): the tilting pod only.
# Authored centred on the OBJ origin so animation.frames can tilt it about
# its own centre (pitch about +Z, roll about +X) and lift it onto its
# cradle. The boarding stairs are base-game graphics, so the object
# provides only the pod; 4 view directions x 35 tilt poses.
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
mtllib materials.mtl

